      "exp": "「RADSTER」的臨床詮釋：SBRT 與 RFA for small renal tumors both 帶來 極佳 結果 in 此 small 研究. RFA 曾有 較少 post-biopsy residual disease, 但 LC 為 still 100% in both 組.",
      "exp_en": "Clinical interpretation of \"RADSTER\": SBRT and RFA for small renal tumors both lead to excellent outcomes in this small study. RFA had less post-biopsy residual disease, but LC was still 100% in both arms.",
