      "ans": "C",
      "exp": "「Princess Margaret Cancer」的臨床詮釋：In 此 統合分析 SBRT 似乎 至 有 better 局部控制 相較於 RFA, microwave ablation, 與 cryotherapy. All 似乎 be 有效 治療 approaches.",
      "exp_en": "Clinical interpretation of \"Princess Margaret Cancer\": In this meta-analysis SBRT seems to have better local control compared to RFA, microwave ablation, and cryotherapy. All seem to be effective treatment approaches.",
