      "C_en": "In this meta-analysis SBRT seems to have better local control compared to RFA, microwave ablation, and cryotherapy. All seem to be effective treatment approaches.",
      "D": "此 統合分析 shows 較佳 結果 for both 根治性膀胱切除 與 bladder preservation. OS 似乎 至 favor bladder preservation. 研究 為 limited by its 回溯性 nature. 隨機分配 試驗 為 值得進一步研究.",
